data.description: Make this 5 bedroom 2 bathroom home yours today! This home features spacious bedroom, formal dining room, unique circular shower (2nd floor), hardwood floors throughout, fresh paint and so much more. Conveniently located close to shopping centers, Fort Eustis military base, and approximately 15 minutes from Yorktown beach. Also features spacious back yard for cookouts and gatherings. Make this your first stop today.
